title: Bobby Encounters Tornado Weather On Beach Getaway + We Found Out Why Jordan Davis Charges $100 On Cameo + Lunchbox Tries To Buy Dog In Craigslist Ad Background
itunes:title: Bobby Encounters Tornado Weather On Beach Getaway + We Found Out Why Jordan Davis Charges $100 On Cameo + Lunchbox Tries To Buy Dog In Craigslist Ad Background
description:
Bobby talks about he and Caitlin’s beach getaway where they encountered some unexpected bad weather. We talk to Jordan Davis and find out the real reason he charges $100 to make personalized videos for fans on Cameo. Lunchbox found a Craigslist ad for a run. He called but instead of wanting to buy the run…he asks if the woman would sell him the dog that was sitting on the rug instead.
